 It is about two people who share the grief       
 of losing the person they love.Sid, working in an
 ad agency as a copyright executive lives a lavish
 lifestyle.His divorcee mother lives in Delhi     
 and father lives in US with some woman named     
 Claudia.When Sid dies in an accident, his        
 mother reaches Kolkata to carry his last remains.
 There he meets Sid's colleague,Shahana (Raima    
 Sen) and Ornob (Rituparno Ghosh) who extend      
 support during her stay and help with office     
 procedures.She also comes to know about her      
 son's sexual preference.                         






